    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s a total gem and has been babied since the day it left the lot. It looks and feels just like it did on day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it drives like an absolute dream! If you've been looking for that perfect ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership stress, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
