      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component and amenity functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history performed strictly at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow and has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. This is a collector-grade example intended for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
